Package: targetesme
Title: Collection of R functions implementing target trial emulation in the French ESME database 
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors: Alison Antoine, Youenn Drouet
Description: Collection of R functions developped during the Alison Antoine PhD thesis (2021-2024) that helps implementing target trial emulation methodology in the French ESME database.
